            "text": "Coupon applied to any basket via unverified basket id  [CVSS 4.3: CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:L/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:L/A:N]"
          },
          "locations": [
            {
              "physicalLocation": {
